-- Sears Holdings Agrees to Buy Sears Canada Stake from Pershing Square Fund
-- JoAnne Norton
-- 2010-04-23T10:04:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-04-23/sears-holdings-agrees-to-buy-sears-canada-stake-from-pershing-square-fund.html

          
          
             Sears Holdings Corp. said it agreed
to buy another 18.6 million shares of Sears Canada Inc. for C$30
each from Pershing Square Capital Management LP funds, or about
17.3 percent of the outstanding shares of Sears Canada. That
will give Sears Holdings 97.3 million shares of Sears Canada, or
90.4 percent.  
          
          


  


        